# Cloudflare Pages Redirects & Proxy Rules
# Proxy API, User, Shop, AI routes directly to the Render Backend service
/api/*          https://dundoo-main.onrender.com/api/:splat   200
/user/*         https://dundoo-main.onrender.com/user/:splat  200
/shop/*         https://dundoo-main.onrender.com/shop/:splat  200
/ai/*           https://dundoo-main.onrender.com/ai/:splat    200
/dundoo-dashboard https://dundoo-main.onrender.com/dundoo-dashboard 200

# Fallback proxy for dynamic routes
/*              https://dundoo-main.onrender.com/:splat       200
